title: What is the cringiest Kpop song? - Quora

response.answer_text: Catallena - Orange Caramel (Actually a lot of songs from Orange Caramel) The music video is so weird, they are literally sushi.  Bar Bar Bar - Crayon Pop (And some other songs too) The jumping and just the whole song in general.  I’m Gonna Be A Star - Twice I’m gonna be star~  Who’s Your Mama? - J.Y. Park JYP what the hell? This creepy…  Tilting My Head - Girl’s Day What happened to their clothes?

Actually, I don’t know a ton of cringy Kpop songs, but off the top of my head, the weirdest one I’ve seen (that I remember vividly), is this one:  Okay, I understand most things, but it’s like..SM took drugs and made a nonsensical MV consisting of lyrics like, “ABABABABABBABBAABABBABABA.” (I applaud SM for their deep lyrics and song writing abilities!)
